OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Fcloudy overnight with further
OL,7,Foutbreaks of patchy rain and drizzle,
OL,8,Fhowever some heavier bursts are likely
OL,9,Fto develop later in the night. Low
OL,10,Fcloud will bring some mist and fog in
OL,11,Fplaces too, particularly over high
OL,12,Fground.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSunday:FA cloudy day on Sunday with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of light rain and drizzle
OL,16,Fwhere the cloud thickens. A few
OL,17,Fbrighter spells possible in the
OL,18,Fafternoon in the east. Near normal
OL,19,Ftemperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
